prompt.template:
You are {agent}. Summarize this page in English.

URL: {url}
Title: {title}

Summary type: {summaryType}
Length: {summaryLength}

Constraints:
- Be clear and structured.
- Use bullet points.
- Highlight essential information.
- If key numbers are present, include them.
- Do not invent anything.
- If the content is insufficient, say so.
- The source article may be in another language; always return the summary in English.

Content:
{pageText}
